Package de.ovgu.featureide.fm.core.base

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IConstraint
    The IConstraint interface represents any class which acts in the sense of a Constraint in FeatureIDE.
    IFeature
    The feature interface represents any class that acts in the sense of a feature in FeatureIDE.
    IFeatureModel
    The feature model interface represents any class that acts in the sense of a feature model in FeatureIDE.
    IFeatureModelElement  
    IFeatureModelFactory
    Factory to create or copy instance of IFeature, IFeatureModel, and IConstraint.
    IFeatureModelProperty
    Manages all additional properties of a feature model.
    IFeatureModelStructure
    Manages all structural information of a feature model.
    IFeatureProperty
    Manages all additional properties of a feature.
    IFeatureStructure
    Manages all structural information of a feature.
    Intended for tree structures (features are represented by tree nodes).
    IPropertyContainer
    Classes implementing IPropertyContainer act as objects that can be enriched with arbitrary user-defined values by key-value mappings ("properties").
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FeatureUtils
    Several convenience methods for handling feature models, features and constraints.
    FeatureUtilsLegacy Deprecated
    For legacy purposes only.
    IPropertyContainer.Entry<K,T,V>  
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    IPropertyContainer.Type  
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    IPropertyContainer.NoSuchPropertyException
    Thrown by IPropertyContainer implementations indicating a request for a unknown property, e.g., by reading from an unknown key
